  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare the use of absorbable tackers versus permanent tack fixation using a polyester
      large pore mesh in laparoscopic midline ventral hernia repair in a multicenter (Belgian)
      prospective randomized single-blinded trial.

      All patients referred for elective midline ventral hernia repair should be assessed for
      eligibility and entered in a study log, detailing all included patients during the study
      period.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
